Gnathosoma . Gnathosomal body 26–29 long, 26–32 wide (
Fig. 1
). Seta ch 1 3–6 long, antero-medial in location; seta ch 2 5–6 long, postero-lateral to ch 1 . Subcapitular setae absent (
